# Partner / target repo state — these dirs hold a partner's audit findings and
# run-state and must NEVER be committed (the skills write them into the TARGET
# repo, not here; this guard is so a contributor working in a target can't leak
# them upstream). Note: skills/security-review-journey/ is a SKILL dir, not state.
.security-review/
docs/security-review/
.claude/
*.jsonl
